text: Mihály Oláh (born 25 January 1949) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Tét
